data.description: Welcome Home to this ADORABLE partially-remodeled Rancher, located in Central Park Subdivision in Pueblo; close to shopping, entertainment, schools, parks, and more! This property has SO many major updates to include: Radon Mitigation System, Upgraded Electrical Panel with 150A Panel, Power Humidifier, Novo 485 HTO Power Water Filtration System, Wifi Capable Thermostat, HVAC Overhaul including Carrier 80% AFUE 2-Stage Variable Speed Furnace, Carrier up to 17 SEER 2-Stage A/C, and HVAC Ducting Improvements, Tankless Hot Water Heater, Whole Home Plumbing Repipe; Newer Laminate Wood Flooring on Main Level, 6ft Cedar Privacy Fence, Carport Gate for Privacy, Kitchen Sink Garbage Disposal, newer Interior Paint, and more!!  This 3 bedroom cutie is light and bright and has room for your personal touches and updates! The kitchen has a full suite of appliances, solid surface countertops, gas range oven, and a breakfast bar! The large bonus family/recreation room can be also used for office space, living space; or extra storage! The laundry room is also on the main level; with cabinetry for organization of your laundry items!  The 3-Car attached covered carport has plenty of room for your vehicles and toys! The backyard is spacious with lots of privacy; and a large storage shed! This charming gem also has a 3/4 bath on the upper level that is unfinished; with materials on site.  Do not miss your opportunity; come see it today!
